    <item>
      <title>随着关系改善，中国取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-scraps-tariffs-on-australian-wine-as-relations-improve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国取消了对澳大利亚葡萄酒出口的惩罚性关税，标志着对堪培拉长达三年的贸易压力运动的结束，并为这个价值数十亿美元的行业复兴带来了希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-scraps-tariffs-on-australian-wine-as-relations-improve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 07:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼注资 7.99 亿美元，增持 Ambuja 水泥股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/adani-family-injects-799-million-lifts-stake-in-ambuja-cements</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 及其家人注资 7.99 亿美元增持 Ambuja Cements Ltd. 股份，这位商业大亨在印度基础设施繁荣之际表现出对其水泥业务的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/adani-family-injects-799-million-lifts-stake-in-ambuja-cements</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
